 3 files changed, 3 insertions(+)

--- a/security/Kconfig
+++ b/security/Kconfig
@@ -124,6 +124,7 @@ config SECURITY_DEFAULT_MMAP_MIN_ADDR
 
 source security/selinux/Kconfig
 source security/smack/Kconfig
